name: Server side of fix for Cf's DDoS protection's false positive
body: Note this is released from issue3071, not valencia.

name: checkfallbacks takes new json format
body: This is a release to make checkfallbacks accept the new uniformized json format for the list of fallbacks to check.

name: peerscanner: disable cloudfront
body: This release temporarily disables cloudfront support in peerscanner, since we weren't using it, it was causing test errors, and possibly higher resource usage.

name: Flashlight country blacklist
body: Make flashlight use a country blacklist, as opposed to whitelist.

name: checkfallbacks
body: Release program to check that we can proxy through fallback (chained) proxies.

name: Emergency release to bring back flashlight to our proxies
body: Note that this binary doesn't correspond to this commit.  This is a last-known-good version (corresponding to release 0.0.17, I think) while we debug excessive CPU usage in the current version.

name: cfrjanitor pre-release
body: This is just for internal testing of the lantern_aws deployment.
